<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>PRISM Alert</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            width: 500px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 23.44px;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-underline-position: from-font;
            text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
        }
        .header {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        .content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .table-container {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .table-container th, .table-container td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .table-container th {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
        }
        .button {
            align-self: center;
            display: block;
            width: max-content;
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(99, 178, 189, 1);
            color: black;
            padding: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }
        .readiness-icon{
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background-color:rgba(99, 178, 189, 1);
        }
        .activation-icon{
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background-color:rgba(230, 55, 1, 1);
        }

        .trigger-title {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="title">PRISM</div>
        <div class="header">Activation Triggers activated (<%= windspeed %>) for <%= cycloneName %></div>

        <p>ANTICIPATORY ACTION ALERT FOR TROPICAL STORM <%= cycloneName %> - <%= triggerTime %> - 
            FORECAST BY REGIONAL SPECIALIZED METEOROLOGICAL CENTER LA REUNION</p>
        <div class="content">
            <p><div class="trigger-title"><div class="readiness-icon" > </div>Readiness Trigger Activated </div><br>
                <%= triggerTime %> there was 20% likelihood of Mozambique experiencing tropical storm-force winds within the next 5 days</p>
            
            
            

            <p><div class="trigger-title"><div class="activation-icon" > </div>Activation Triggers: Activated</div><br>
                projected windspedds affecting districts in the next 72 hours:</p>

                <table class="table-container">
                    <tr>
                        <td>> 89 km/h</td>
                        <td><%= districts1 %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>> 118 km/h</td>
                        <td><%= districts2 %></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            
            <a href="<%= urlWithParams %>" class="button">ACCESS PRISM TROPICAL STORM DASHBOARD</a>
            
            <h3>Trajectory Map</h3>
            <img src="data:image/png;base64,<%= base64Image %>" alt="Storm Trajectory" width="100%" style="border-radius: 5px;">
            <a href="<%= urlWithParams %>" class="button">ACCESS PRISM TROPICAL STORM DASHBOARD</a>
            
            <p>We will continue to closely monitor the situation and provide timely updates as more information becomes available.<br>
                Best regards,<br>
                WFP Mozambique Country Office</p>
            
            <p><strong>WFP Mozambique Country Office</strong></p>
            
            <div class="footer">
                This message was automatically generated.<br>
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe here</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
